{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01NAbBXYsJezpxmgbSyJaxSK","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→use anchor_lang::prelude::*;\n     2→use rng_shared::lifecycle::RoundPhase;\n     3→\n     4→/// Global configuration for the coinflip program.\n     5→/// PDA seeds: [b\"coinflip_config\"]\n     6→#[account]\n     7→#[derive(InitSpace)]\n     8→pub struct CoinflipConfig {\n     9→    /// Admin authority (can update config).\n    10→    pub authority: Pubkey,\n    11→    /// Fee destination wallet.\n    12→    pub treasury: Pubkey,\n    13→    /// Whether the game is paused (rejects new matches).\n    14→    pub paused: bool,\n    15→    /// Bump seed for PDA derivation.\n    16→    pub bump: u8,\n    17→}\n    18→\n    19→/// A coinflip match between two players.\n    20→/// PDA seeds: [b\"match\", creator.key().as_ref()]\n    21→#[account]\n    22→#[derive(InitSpace)]\n    23→pub struct CoinflipMatch {\n    24→    /// The player who created the match.\n    25→    pub creator: Pubkey,\n    26→    /// The player who joined (Pubkey::default() if empty).\n    27→    pub opponent: Pubkey,\n    28→    /// Tier index (0-5).\n    29→    pub tier: u8,\n    30→    /// Entry amount in lamports (derived from tier).\n    31→    pub entry_amount: u64,\n    32→    /// Side chosen by creator (0 = Heads, 1 = Tails).\n    33→    pub creator_side: u8,\n    34→    /// Current phase of the match (shared lifecycle enum).\n    35→    pub phase: RoundPhase,\n    36→    /// The winning side after VRF resolution (0 or 1, only valid when settled).\n    37→    pub result: u8,\n    38→    /// The winner's pubkey (Pubkey::default() until settled).\n    39→    pub winner: Pubkey,\n    40→    /// Whether the payout has been claimed.\n    41→    pub claimed: bool,\n    42→    /// Unix timestamp when the match was created.\n    43→    pub created_at: i64,\n    44→    /// Unix timestamp when the match entered LOCKED phase (0 if still WAITING).\n    45→    pub locked_at: i64,\n    46→    /// Deadline for VRF resolution; after this, timeout refund is available.\n    47→    pub resolve_deadline: i64,\n    48→    /// Address of the Orao randomness PDA for VRF lookup at claim time.\n    49→    pub vrf_request_key: Pubkey,\n    50→    /// Bump seed for PDA derivation.\n    51→    pub bump: u8,\n    52→}\n    53→\n    54→/// Event emitted when a match is settled via claim_payout.\n    55→#[event]\n    56→pub struct MatchSettled {\n    57→    pub creator: Pubkey,\n    58→    pub opponent: Pubkey,\n    59→    pub winner: Pubkey,\n    60→    pub randomness: [u8; 32],\n    61→    pub payout_amount: u64,\n    62→    pub fee_amount: u64,\n    63→    pub vrf_request_key: Pubkey,\n    64→}\n    65→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01BcRDdFAHtegqoVKFVRRjBv","session_id":"78853bc0-87e2-4084-ac9d-e40a4ee398e1","uuid":"08188334-5e06-489b-a40b-f97473508f3a"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01BcRDdFAHtegqoVKFVRRjBv","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I've gathered all the key contents from the files you requested. Here's a comprehensive summary organized by file:\n\n## Summary of Key Contents\n\n### 1. **`sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/utils/chain.ts`**\n\n**Program IDs and Imports:**\n```typescript\nconst COINFLIP_PROGRAM_ID = new PublicKey(\n  (import.meta as unknown as { env: Record<string, string | undefined> }).env\n    .VITE_COINFLIP_PROGRAM_ID ?? CoinflipIDL.address\n);\nconst ORAO_VRF_PROGRAM_ID = new PublicKey(\"VRFzZoJdhFWL8rkvu87LpKM3RbcVezpMEc6X5GVDr7y\");\n\n// Imports from anchor-client and game-engine\nimport { CoinflipIDL, type Coinflip } from \"@rng-utopia/anchor-client\";\nimport { TIER_VALUES, COIN_SIDE_VALUES, TIER_AMOUNTS } from \"@rng-utopia/game-engine/browser\";\n```\n\n**Key PDA Derivation Functions:**\n- `getMatchPda(creator: PublicKey)` — Seeds: `[\"match\", creator]`\n- `getConfigPda()` — Seeds: `[\"coinflip_config\"]`\n- `getOraoNetworkStatePda()` — Orao VRF network state\n- `getOraoRandomnessPda(seed: Uint8Array)` — Derived from match PDA\n\n**OnChainMatch Interface** (important field):\n```typescript\ninterface OnChainMatch {\n  vrfRequestKey: PublicKey;  // Orao randomness PDA address\n  // ... other fields\n}\n```\n\n### 2. **`sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/types.ts`**\n\n**UIMatch Type** (Frontend representation):\n```typescript\nexport interface UIMatch {\n  id: string;\n  tier: Tier;\n  player1: string; // wallet address\n  player1Side: CoinSide;\n  player2: string | null;\n  phase: CoinflipPhase;\n  result: CoinSide | null;\n  winner: string | null;\n  claimed: boolean;\n  payoutAmount: number;\n  seedHash: string;      // SHA-256 hash of server seed (shown before flip)\n  serverSeed?: string;   // Actual server seed (revealed only after settlement)\n  vrfProof?: string;     // VRF proof for on-chain verification\n  blockHash?: string;    // Solana blockhash used as entropy source\n}\n```\n\n### 3. **`sources/rng-utopia/packages/anchor-client/src/coinflip.ts`**\n\n**MatchSettled Event Type Definition:**\n```typescript\n{\n  \"name\": \"matchSettled\",\n  \"type\": {\n    \"kind\": \"struct\",\n    \"fields\": [\n      { \"name\": \"creator\", \"type\": \"pubkey\" },\n      { \"name\": \"opponent\", \"type\": \"pubkey\" },\n      { \"name\": \"winner\", \"type\": \"pubkey\" },\n      { \"name\": \"randomness\", \"type\": { \"array\": [\"u8\", 32] } },\n      { \"name\": \"payoutAmount\", \"type\": \"u64\" },\n      { \"name\": \"feeAmount\", \"type\": \"u64\" },\n      { \"name\": \"vrfRequestKey\", \"type\": \"pubkey\" }  // KEY FIELD\n    ]\n  }\n}\n\n// Also on CoinflipMatch account:\n{\n  \"name\": \"vrfRequestKey\",\n  \"docs\": [\"Address of the Orao randomness PDA for VRF lookup at claim time.\"],\n  \"type\": \"pubkey\"\n}\n```\n\n### 4. **`sources/rng-utopia/packages/anchor-client/src/index.ts`**\n\n**Export Structure:**\n```typescript\nimport CoinflipIDL from \"./coinflip.json\" with { type: \"json\" };\nimport PlatformIDL from \"./platform.json\" with { type: \"json\" };\n\nexport type { Coinflip } from \"./coinflip.js\";\nexport type { Platform } from \"./platform.js\";\nexport { CoinflipIDL, PlatformIDL };\n```\n\n### 5. **`sources/rng-utopia/packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts`**\n\n**Key Function for Fairness Verification:**\n```typescript\nexport function determineWinnerFromRandomness(\n  randomness: Uint8Array,\n  player1Side: CoinSide\n): { result: CoinSide; player1Wins: boolean } {\n  // Match the on-chain logic: first byte % 2\n  const firstByte = randomness[0] ?? 0;\n  const result: CoinSide = firstByte % 2 === 0 ? \"heads\" : \"tails\";\n  const player1Wins = player1Side === result;\n  return { result, player1Wins };\n}\n\n// Also exports:\nexport const COINFLIP_PROGRAM_ID = new PublicKey(\"H8Q2R1bUxzfUkV6WRRiZxYWwGfCr794AcnskWpsRQJf3\");\nexport function getMatchPda(creator: PublicKey): [PublicKey, number];\nexport function getConfigPda(): [PublicKey, number];\nexport function calculatePotentialPayout(tier: Tier): number;\n```\n\n### 6. **`sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/coinflip/src/instructions/claim_payout.rs`**\n\n**How MatchSettled Event Is Emitted:**\n```rust\n// (2) Read Orao randomness\nlet randomness = read_orao_randomness(&ctx.accounts.randomness_account)?;\n\n// (3) Derive winner from randomness\nlet result = from_randomness(randomness[0]);  // Uses shared function\nlet winner = if result == coinflip_match.creator_side {\n    coinflip_match.creator\n} else {\n    coinflip_match.opponent\n};\n\n// (4) Compute fee/payout\nlet pool = coinflip_match.entry_amount.checked_mul(2).unwrap();\nlet (fee, payout) = calculate_net_payout(pool);\n\n// (7) Emit MatchSettled event\nemit!(MatchSettled {\n    creator: coinflip_match.creator,\n    opponent: coinflip_match.opponent,\n    winner,\n    randomness,           // Full 32-byte randomness array\n    payout_amount: payout,\n    fee_amount: fee,\n    vrf_request_key: coinflip_match.vrf_request_key,\n});\n```\n\n### 7. **`sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/coinflip/src/state.rs`**\n\n**MatchSettled Event Definition (Rust):**\n```rust\n#[event]\npub struct MatchSettled {\n    pub creator: Pubkey,\n    pub opponent: Pubkey,\n    pub winner: Pubkey,\n    pub randomness: [u8; 32],      // Full randomness bytes from Orao VRF\n    pub payout_amount: u64,\n    pub fee_amount: u64,\n    pub vrf_request_key: Pubkey,   // Links to Orao randomness account\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Key Findings for Your Fairness Verification Utility\n\nYou have everything needed to build a verification utility:\n\n1. **Randomness Source**: Full 32-byte randomness array available in `MatchSettled` event\n2. **Fairness Logic**: `determineWinnerFromRandomness()` uses `randomness[0] % 2` (on-chain logic at `rng_shared::constants::from_randomness`)\n3. **VRF Linking**: `vrfRequestKey` field connects the match to the Orao randomness account for proof verification\n4. **Payout Verification**: Both `payoutAmount` and `feeAmount` emitted in event allow fee calculation auditing\n5. **Event Data**: Complete player pubkeys, winner, and timestamps available for audit trail\n\nThe utility should verify:\n- Randomness matches on-chain via `vrfRequestKey` → Orao account lookup\n- Winner determination matches using `first_byte % 2 == 0 ? \"heads\" : \"tails\"`\n- Payout calculation: `pool = entry_amount * 2; (fee, payout) = calculate_net_payout(pool)`\n- All parties present and correctly identified"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a1dc0586e45697d55 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 49371\ntool_uses: 7\nduration_ms: 23819</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"78853bc0-87e2-4084-ac9d-e40a4ee398e1","uuid":"82bb56d9-bd11-44b8-b153-2b10a2de0105","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"I need to build a fairness verification utility for a coinflip game. Explore these files and return their key contents:\n\n1. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/utils/chain.ts` - How existing chain utils are structured, program IDs, imports\n2. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/types.ts` - Frontend types\n3. `sources/rng-utopia/packages/anchor-client/src/coinflip.ts` - Look for `MatchSettled` event type definition, especially the `vrfRequestKey` field\n4. `sources/rng-utopia/packages/anchor-client/src/index.ts` - How IDL/types are exported\n5. `sources/rng-utopia/packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts` - Look for `determineWinnerFromRandomness` or `from_randomness` equivalent\n6. `sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/coinflip/src/instructions/claim_payout.rs` - How the MatchSettled event is emitted, what fields it has\n7. `sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/coinflip/src/state.rs` - MatchSettled event definition\n\nReturn the relevant code sections from each file - imports, exports, type definitions, key function signatures. Focus on what I need to build the verification utility.","agentId":"a1dc0586e45697d55","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I've gathered all the key contents from the files you requested. Here's a comprehensive summary organized by file:\n\n## Summary of Key Contents\n\n### 1. **`sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/utils/chain.ts`**\n\n**Program IDs and Imports:**\n```typescript\nconst COINFLIP_PROGRAM_ID = new PublicKey(\n  (import.meta as unknown as { env: Record<string, string | undefined> }).env\n    .VITE_COINFLIP_PROGRAM_ID ?? CoinflipIDL.address\n);\nconst ORAO_VRF_PROGRAM_ID = new PublicKey(\"VRFzZoJdhFWL8rkvu87LpKM3RbcVezpMEc6X5GVDr7y\");\n\n// Imports from anchor-client and game-engine\nimport { CoinflipIDL, type Coinflip } from \"@rng-utopia/anchor-client\";\nimport { TIER_VALUES, COIN_SIDE_VALUES, TIER_AMOUNTS } from \"@rng-utopia/game-engine/browser\";\n```\n\n**Key PDA Derivation Functions:**\n- `getMatchPda(creator: PublicKey)` — Seeds: `[\"match\", creator]`\n- `getConfigPda()` — Seeds: `[\"coinflip_config\"]`\n- `getOraoNetworkStatePda()` — Orao VRF network state\n- `getOraoRandomnessPda(seed: Uint8Array)` — Derived from match PDA\n\n**OnChainMatch Interface** (important field):\n```typescript\ninterface OnChainMatch {\n  vrfRequestKey: PublicKey;  // Orao randomness PDA address\n  // ... other fields\n}\n```\n\n### 2. **`sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/coinflip/types.ts`**\n\n**UIMatch Type** (Frontend representation):\n```typescript\nexport interface UIMatch {\n  id: string;\n  tier: Tier;\n  player1: string; // wallet address\n  player1Side: CoinSide;\n  player2: string | null;\n  phase: CoinflipPhase;\n  result: CoinSide | null;\n  winner: string | null;\n  claimed: boolean;\n  payoutAmount: number;\n  seedHash: string;      // SHA-256 hash of server seed (shown before flip)\n  serverSeed?: string;   // Actual server seed (revealed only after settlement)\n  vrfProof?: string;     // VRF proof for on-chain verification\n  blockHash?: string;    // Solana blockhash used as entropy source\n}\n```\n\n### 3. **`sources/rng-utopia/packages/anchor-client/src/coinflip.ts`**\n\n**MatchSettled Event Type Definition:**\n```typescript\n{\n  \"name\": \"matchSettled\",\n  \"type\": {\n    \"kind\": \"struct\",\n    \"fields\": [\n      { \"name\": \"creator\", \"type\": \"pubkey\" },\n      { \"name\": \"opponent\", \"type\": \"pubkey\" },\n      { \"name\": \"winner\", \"type\": \"pubkey\" },\n      { \"name\": \"randomness\", \"type\": { \"array\": [\"u8\", 32] } },\n      { \"name\": \"payoutAmount\", \"type\": \"u64\" },\n      { \"name\": \"feeAmount\", \"type\": \"u64\" },\n      { \"name\": \"vrfRequestKey\", \"type\": \"pubkey\" }  // KEY FIELD\n    ]\n  }\n}\n\n// Also on CoinflipMatch account:\n{\n  \"name\": \"vrfRequestKey\",\n  \"docs\": [\"Address of the Orao randomness PDA for VRF lookup at claim time.\"],\n  \"type\": \"pubkey\"\n}\n```\n\n### 4. **`sources/rng-utopia/packages/anchor-client/src/index.ts`**\n\n**Export Structure:**\n```typescript\nimport CoinflipIDL from \"./coinflip.json\" with { type: \"json\" };\nimport PlatformIDL from \"./platform.json\" with { type: \"json\" };\n\nexport type { Coinflip } from \"./coinflip.js\";\nexport type { Platform } from \"./platform.js\";\nexport { CoinflipIDL, PlatformIDL };\n```\n\n### 5. **`sources/rng-utopia/packages/game-engine/src/coinflip.ts`**\n\n**Key Function for Fairness Verification:**\n```typescript\nexport function determineWinnerFromRandomness(\n  randomness: Uint8Array,\n  player1Side: CoinSide\n): { result: CoinSide; player1Wins: boolean } {\n  // Match the on-chain logic: first byte % 2\n  const firstByte = randomness[0] ?? 0;\n  const result: CoinSide = firstByte % 2 === 0 ? \"heads\" : \"tails\";\n  const player1Wins = player1Side === result;\n  return { result, player1Wins };\n}\n\n// Also exports:\nexport const COINFLIP